<p class="body">The direct signup model is a small operational lift compared to network programs (you manage the relationship and payouts separately from your other programs), but it eliminates the network's cut of the commission and gives you direct access to the brand for asset requests, sample bags, and custom co-marketing. For organic-focused, sustainability-focused, or wellness-focused content, this is the first program to sign up for.</p>

